---
title: Double Sweet & Salty Popcorn Chicken with Garlic Rice & Sesame Veggies
description: Tonight’s chicken is really ‘popping off’ (please forgive the pun). A touch of sweet and a zap of salty and you’ve got
chicken that will be popping with flavour (sorry we couldn’t help it). Fragrant garlic rice helps to absorb the sauces
and sesame veggies. It’s bound to be a pop-ular dish (okay we’re done now).
